            <div id="about">
                <h2>About this recipe</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><b>Source: </b> Modified from <a href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/1941631045/ref=as_li_qf_asin_il_tl?ie=UTF8&creative=9325&creativeASIN=1941631045">Plant Powered Familes by Dreena Burton (Amazon link)</a>, Easy Being Green Smoothie (page 40)</li>
                    <li>This recipe can be flexible (substitute different greens or fruit chunks)
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div id="planning">
                <h2>Planning</h2>
                <p><b>Prep Time:</b> 5 minutes</p>
                <p><b>Cook Time:</b> 0 minutes</p>
                <p><b>Servings:</b> 4 <p>
            </div> 

            <div id="preparation">
                <h2>Preparation</h2>
                <h3>Equipment</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Blender</li>
                    
                </ul>
                <h3>Ingredients</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Spinach, 3 packed cups</li>
                    <li>Frozen mango, 1 cup</li>
                    <li>Orange, 1 peeled</li>
                    <li>Banan slices (fresh or frozen), 1 cup</li>
                    <li>Cucumber, chunks, 1 cup</li>
                    <li>Protein powder, unflavored, 1-2 tablespoons</li>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Our preferred protein powder: <a href="https://sunwarrior.com/products/classic-plus-protein-unflavored">Sun Warrior Unflavored</a></li>
                    </ul>
                    <li>Hemp seeds, 2 Tbsp</li>
                    <li>Water, 1 cup</li>
                    
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div id="cooking">
                <h2>Cooking</h2>
                <ol>
                    <li>Add all ingredients to blender, blend until smooth</li>
                    
                </ol>

            </div>

            <div id="notes">
                <h2>Notes & Tips</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Yum</li>
                    <li>Can use kale instead of spinach</li>
                    <li>1 cup frozen pineapple chunks can be substituted for the orange</li>
                </ul>

            </div>

            <div id="Nutrition">
